ked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>AD324</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Karanis</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Διοσκόρῳ πραιποσίτῳ <expan><ex cert="high">πέμπτου</ex></expan> πάγου 

    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>σιδώ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear>ου Πτολεμαίου ἀπὸ κώμης Καρανίδος.  κέκτημαι ἀρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ού</unclear>-

    <lb n="3"/>ρας ὑπὲρ τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὰς</unclear> ὀγ<g type="apostrophe"/>δοήκοντα <num value="80"/>, ὑπὲρ ὧν μὴ <subst><add place="inline">σπειρομένων</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">σπιρομενων</del></subst> τὰ τῷ ταμείῳ 

    <lb n="4"/>πολλῷ χρόνῳ τελῶ καὶ τούτων <choice><corr>ἕνεκα</corr><sic>ενεγκα</sic></choice> εἰς πενίαν περιέστην. μά-

    <lb n="5"/>λ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear> γὰρ μόλις μετὰ τοσούτων καμάτων καὶ ἀναλωμάτων ἀπὸ τού-

    <lb n="6"/>τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ω</unclear>ν ἐν σί<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied>ῳ μόνας ἀρούρας ὀκτὼ <num value="8"/> <choice><corr>κατέσπειρα</corr><sic>κατεσπιρα</sic></choice> καὶ χορτοσπέρμο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υ</unclear> 

    <lb n="7"/>ἀρούρας δύο <num value="2"/>.  ἐπεὶ οὖν ἅμα τῇ φυῇ τούτων Ἀμμωνᾶς Καπέει καὶ 

    <lb n="8"/>Σαμβάθιον <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Σ</unclear>υρίωνος καὶ Σωτᾶς Ἀχιλλᾶ καὶ Πτολλᾶς Ἀρίστωνος τὰς 

    <lb n="9"/>ἑαυτ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῶ</unclear>ν βοῦς ἐπαφῆ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>αν ταῖς ἐν σίτῳ καὶ ταύτας καταβεβρώκασιν, 

    <lb n="10"/>καὶ τότε βιβ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>ί<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear> σοι περὶ τούτου ἐπιδέδωκα.  ἀλλ᾽ <choice><corr>ὕστερον</corr><sic>οιστερον</sic></choice> <choice><corr>αὐξησά<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">μ</supplied>ενα</corr><sic>αυξησαεν<add place="supralinear">α</add></sic></choice> 

    <lb n="11"/>καὶ καρπὸν <choice><corr>δεδωκότα</corr><sic><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δεδ</unclear>ωκω<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>α</sic></choice> καὶ εἰς ἀκμὴν ἔλθοντα, πρὶν θερισθῆ-

    <lb n="12"/>ναι, πάλιν οἱ αὐτοὶ ἐπιβουλεύοντές μοι καὶ μεγά<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λα</unclear> <choice><corr>δυνάμενοι</corr><sic>δυνομενοι</sic></choice> ἐπὶ 

    <lb n="13"/>τῶν τόπων, βουλόμενοί <choice><corr>με</corr><sic>μαι</sic></choice> τὴν <hi rend="diaeresis">ἰ</hi>δίαν <choice><corr>ἐγκαταλεῖψαι</corr><sic>ενκαταλιψε</sic></choice>, τὰς αὐτὰς βοῦς 

    <lb n="14"/>εἰς τὸν σπό<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear>ον παραστήσαντες, <choice><corr>τέλειον</corr><sic>τελαιον</sic></choice> καταβρωθῆναι ἐπέ-

    <lb n="15"/>τρεψαν ὡς μηδὲ<add place="supralinear">ν</add> τὸ σύνολον <choice><corr>ἐκεῖσε</corr><sic>εκισαι</sic></choice> εὑρίσκεσθαι οὐδὲν δὲ ἧ<hi rend="diaeresis">τ</hi>τον 

    <lb n="16"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>αὶ Ἅρπαλος ποιμὴν εἰς τὸν χορτόσπερμον καὶ τὸν χόρτον τὸν 

    <lb n="17"/><choice><corr>κοπέντα</corr><sic>κωπεντα</sic></choice> καὶ <choice><corr>ἀποκείμενον</corr><sic>απο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>ιμενον</sic></choice> <add place="supralinear">ἐν τῷ πεδίῳ</add> ἐπαφῆκεν τὰ ἑαυτοῦ θρέμματα καὶ ταῦ-

    <lb n="18"/>τα καταβεβρώκασιν.  καὶ διὰ τοῦτο ἀποσιωπᾶν μὴ <choice><corr>δυνάμενος</corr><sic>δυνομενος</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="19"/>τῶν <choice><corr>μειζόνων</corr><sic>μιζονων</sic></choice> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear>ο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>λάκις προσταξάντων τὰ <choice><corr>καταλαμβανόμενα</corr><sic>κα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>αλαμβανωμενα</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="20"/>ζῷα ἀδ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>κοῦντα ἀλλοτρίου<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>αρποὺς ταῦτα <choice><corr>καταπωλεῖσθαι</corr><sic>καταπωλισθαι</sic></choice> καὶ 

    <lb n="21"/>τῷ μὲν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>αμείῳ μ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">έ</unclear>ρος <choice><corr>χωρεῖν</corr><sic>χωριν</sic></choice> καὶ τῷ τὴν βλάβην πεπονθότι 

    <lb n="22"/>τὸ ἄλλο μέρος, με<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ὰ τοῦ καὶ κίνδυνον ἐκδέξασθαι τοὺς τού-

    <lb n="23"/>των νομέας ἤτοι δεσπότας, τὰ βιβλία ἐπιδίδωμι ἀξιῶν ἀχθῆ-

    <lb n="24"/>ναι αὐτοὺς ἐπὶ σο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῦ</unclear> καὶ τῇ <choice><corr>ἀκολουθίᾳ</corr><sic>ακαλουθια</sic></choice> χρήσασ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θα</unclear>ι. διευτύχει. 

    <lb n="25"/>τοῖς ἐσομένοις ὑπάτοις τὸ <expan><ex cert="high">τέταρτον</ex></expan>, Παῦνι <num value="6">ϛ</num>, 

    <lb n="26"/><hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>σίδωρος ἐπ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>δέδωκα. Ἥρων ἔγραψα ὑπὲρ αὐτοῦ <choice><corr>ἀγρ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">α</supplied>μμάτου</corr><sic>αγρμματου</sic></choice>. </ab></div><div n="meta.11940" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.11940" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="324" notBefore="324" type="textDate" value="0324-05-31">31. Mai 324</date></p></div><div n="meta.11940" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Archiv des Aurelius Isidoros.</p></div><div n="meta.11940" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Merton</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">92</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">11940</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0159</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">92</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0159;2;92" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.11940" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">XL nach S. 166</bibl><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Montevecchi, Papirologia, Tav. 85</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.11940" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">C.Pap.Jud. III 518d</bibl></div><div n="meta.11940" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" su